<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- Phrases 1+2 (mm. 1-12): Structural repeat. F# major chord → F#m(vi) throughout.
  LH uses P5+P4+m3 voicings: A2-E3-A3-C#4 for I, F#2-C#3-F#3-A3 for vi.
- Phrase 3 (mm. 13-18): Development. Sus4 suspension on A (bar 14), high-register
  F#m-C#m-F#m sequence (bar 15), 8th-note chord changes (bar 18).
- Phrase 4 (mm. 19-24): Final phrase. Sus2 suspension (bar 23), D(IV) pivot
  in bar 22 for authentic cadential IV→I color.

VOICE LEADING HIGHLIGHTS:
- F#m→E (bars 3, 9): RH A4-C#5 → G#4-B4, LH A3 → G#3, stepwise parallel 3rds.
- Bar 14: Asus4 D5 (upper P4) resolves to C#5, inner step D→C#.
- Bar 18: rapid 8th-note C#m-A-F#m — LH pedal on A2-E3-A3 held through.
- Bar 23: Asus2 with B4 tension note releases to C#5 by step.

TEXTURE ARC:
- mm. 1-6: Sparse (half-rests), 2-note RH, 3-4 note LH, meditative A-major
- mm. 7-12: Phrase repeat, slightly fuller RH (C#5-E5 added)
- mm. 13-18: Development — sus4 color, high F#m-C#m, 8th-note motion
- mm. 19-24: Return and climax — F#5 peak, IV→vi→I cadential pattern, final whole note
-->
